entries.femaleVariant: Good evening, Night City! Boy, do I have a treat for you! Make that three treats! On the show we have the girls from... Wait, how do you say it? Ass Cracks? Us Cracks?
Ziggy... You can say it however you want, heheh.
He's pretty cute in person, isn't he?
It's a relief to see you girls in such high spirits. I mean, after someone destroyed your equipment truck, it must've been terrifying.
You are joking? It was wild!
This is why we love Night City. It is so... crazy!
And if a man set fire to your limo right now, what would you say to him?
Invite us with you next time! Pow-boom!
